Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:37.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\1c&H635F64&\pos(441,429)\frz11.01}一起吃蛋糕庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:37.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\1c&H161315&\frz342.5\pos(972,621)}给小树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:37.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\1c&H2E292C&\fs45\pos(474,990)\frz15.71}别管别人怎么看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有大家写来互相加油的信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然纸上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但东乡学姐帮大家画了南瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太可怕了 这不是欺负人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦应该知道什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但他们也说什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们也是这么回答我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦又跟我们装傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看来大赦确实是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我跟我有权交流的神官们问鹫鹫的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家都摇头说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}居然会有大赦都不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我闹了脾气让他们拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦的人就拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用这个去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在还能变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 小鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们看 鹫鹫的手机不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我手机的雷达 也没有探测到鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫可能在一个出乎我们意料的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你的意思是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}墙的外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡这么脱线 的确可能跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以变成勇者去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}变成勇者 还会为力量付出代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听说这次版本更新 没有散花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}简直好到难以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 再怎么更新系统 结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}害怕是当然的 我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 为了找到东乡 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这和第一次的时候不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我作为部长 不希望大家轻易就变身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请不要冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们的确经历过很多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果没有勇者自我牺牲的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界已经毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们也别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦的做法只是不太恰当 但不能怪谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦向我保证 不会再隐瞒勇者系统的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}当面听过后 我决定相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这次我愿意接受 我会去找她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然不是很认识大赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是小园都这么说了 我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐 我想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是的 别丢下部长一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也相信友奈和乃木你们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然有勇者部员失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}同为部员就有责任去找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过要去墙外 就不知道会发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树 先多吃点营养品补身子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这次我吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们真是群好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小园也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}新版勇者系统中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}满开槽从一开始就是满能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}精灵可以张开护罩保护勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但使用护罩会消耗满开槽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而满开槽不能回复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以在满开槽满的时候使用满开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}使用后会消耗全部满开槽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}满开槽消耗完 精灵就不能张开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这时受到攻击就会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是没有散花的勇者系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是像这样把一切都说清楚比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 这样就能做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}事后打扫可能很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}牛鬼 好久不见 请多关照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等一下 看不到前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}它果然还是很粘姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}异端
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}诸行无常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}借踏一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再往前就唔啊啊啊了 大家多小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我打头阵 园子在我背后支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小鱼干 别一个人冲太前面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树 今晚做特制乌冬面给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 我会满心期待的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是这么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么看都不像是同个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雷达上有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是东乡 东乡果然在墙壁外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们有机会 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没想到会这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的是这个方向吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就在那个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 鹫鹫好像就在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡…竟然变成了黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}第一次碰上好久不见的人成了黑洞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}周围有Vertex啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但要怎么过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}偏偏挑这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢了 树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很厉害嘛 园子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}被称赞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但这样下去只会单方面被消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底要怎么去东乡那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}坐天船应该能到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}天船…园子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}满开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你怎么突然就满开了 会没有精灵保护的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我经历过没有护罩的时代 不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是去鹫鹫身边的天船 大家都坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好帅的船哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡园子你们几个真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的才是最帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小园真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你 悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等着我吧 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}各位没有晕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还什么晕不晕的 感觉好不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那里面究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们主动出击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难道他们在保护这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去东乡她那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们一定要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你一定要平安回来 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是部长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}碍事的家伙交给我们解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那里面什么事都有可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拿出气势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}包在我身上 小园
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 一口气冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不会让你妨碍悠悠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}悠悠 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我必须到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灵魂离体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难道…要是我倒在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的身体也会一直留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园上了我们所在的中学后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就发生了大赦未曾预料到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我破坏了一部分结界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}导致外界火焰剧烈的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样下去 外界的火焰将吞噬世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦需要冻结迄今为止的反抗计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}并着手打破现状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是东乡的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 你就在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有别的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要减弱火势 必须举行奉火祭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是将能听到神之声的巫女献给外界的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请求天神原谅的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也是西历纪年结束时举行过的献祭仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在大赦供职的几位巫女 被选作了活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但大赦的人告诉我 我也可以担任这个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为我同时拥有勇者的资格和巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是独一无二的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没什么好烦恼的 是我让结界开了洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一定要为此赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要友奈还有其他人平安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}牺牲我一个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要是消失了 友奈她们一定会来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以神树大人 请不要让她们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡总是这么固执
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}居然自己消去了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我跟你约好的 不会留下你一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以 无论多少次我都会救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果然是那时见到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我这就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这点痛算什么 把东乡放开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一起回去吧 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}成功了 这样就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了 你醒啦 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家…这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你睡了好几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是你们救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但这样下去 世界会被火…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们知道情况了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}火势已经趋于平稳 所以也不需要祭品了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难道说有人代替我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 你好像被夺走了常人会死的生命能量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以你也算完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但你很顽强 所以还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后我们也及时赶到了 差不多这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还好有好好锻炼过身体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}医生说你全身都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真的得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 安全啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦你完成使命咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然还得在医院待上一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这下勇者部再次全员聚齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明约好不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我们却忘了好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我才该道歉 让你们这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没办法嘛 换成是我也会这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}下次碰上这种事 一定要跟我们商量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过就这样扯平不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们的确也忘记过你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但大家最后还是想起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乖 乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}告一段落啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:22:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以全员聚齐过圣诞 除夕和新年啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么全是玩的事啊
Comment: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:43.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}尊き勇者たち　一時の平和が来た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:57.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}何もかもすべてが　眠りにつく時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:10.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}戦った人　涙堪えた人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:21.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}朧げな夢が　迎えに来るでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:33.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}勇敢な人　涙零した人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:37.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}今日はおやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:48.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}寝息を立てたら　夜が包み込む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:43.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}尊贵的勇者们 迎来了短暂的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:57.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}万物沉寂 合上了迷濛的睡眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:10.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}那些战斗的人 噙住眼泪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:21.65,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}也将前往那片 朦胧的梦乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:33.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}那些无畏的人 洒下热泪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:37.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}今天好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:48.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}安心睡吧 深深的黑夜会包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不愧是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太残酷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是灾难啊 灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我好像知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小心别受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}绝对不能把他人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.64,0:24:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐！
